---
/**
 * Villain — the receipts. Centered header, two pull quotes, nothing else.
 * The quotes are the argument; a closing paragraph would be restating.
 */
---
<section class="border-b border-white/5">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div data-reveal class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="mb-4 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-white/55">
        Why this exists
      </p>
      <h2
        class="text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.02em] text-white sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl"
        style="font-family: 'Outfit', 'Inter Variable', sans-serif;"
      >
        Your editor's undo
        <span class="text-white/45">is broken.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div data-reveal class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <figure>
        <blockquote
          class="text-2xl leading-[1.3] font-medium text-white sm:text-3xl"
          style="font-family: 'Outfit', 'Inter Variable', sans-serif;"
        >
          &ldquo;Close the Agent Review Tab before the agent makes edits.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-6 text-sm text-white/55">
          <span class="text-white">deanrie</span>, Cursor staff · Jan 2026 ·
          <a
            href="https://forum.cursor.com/t/agent-code-changes-are-automatically-deleted/149024"
            rel="noopener"
            class="underline decoration-white/20 underline-offset-4 hover:text-white hover:decoration-white/50"
          >forum.cursor.com</a>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure>
        <blockquote
          class="text-2xl leading-[1.3] font-medium text-white sm:text-3xl"
          style="font-family: 'Outfit', 'Inter Variable', sans-serif;"
        >
          &ldquo;<span class="text-white/65">90% of my app is gone.</span>&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-6 text-sm text-white/55">
          <span class="text-white">Jonneal3</span> · May 2025 ·
          <a
            href="https://forum.cursor.com/t/help-needed-asap-cursor-deleted-my-whole-proejct/97589"
            rel="noopener"
            class="underline decoration-white/20 underline-offset-4 hover:text-white hover:decoration-white/50"
          >forum.cursor.com</a>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
